Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:07.88,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…今天上午又舉行「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:16.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧…放暑假之前都舉行好幾次「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:17.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:23.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}因為這裡是個荒僻的小島吧\h\h\h爸爸小時候的畢業典禮也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:29.65,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我「畢業」後會去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:37.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…會陪在爸爸身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.62,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連母親的份一起…直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:42.62,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡也不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:52.55,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐未學姐是主動競選進學生會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.17,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:57.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得很辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:02.47,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個若無其事帶狗來學校還遊手好閒的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:04.98,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:07.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:13.40,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是副會長的工作 還是學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道…兩者都是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:28.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐未…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:37.88,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士同學…令尊常去探望我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:38.72,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.64,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在公事上聽取一些建議…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:43.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fn黑體}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:46.44,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:47.85,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.41,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.95,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）是{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.21,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.71,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.17,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}TSX
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.05,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}TS…X？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）{\fnArial}Fafner Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}祝賀你「畢業」…祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（翔子）啊 將陵學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.45,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 普庫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）我決定…要「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.79,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 幾時？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:39.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假結束後就出島 和大人們一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:44.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長真厲害 我就不敢想什麼工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:48.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的事 羽佐間一定也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.98,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我不在了 你也要記住這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:09.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:09.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）喲 我決定要「畢業」了 來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:14.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（祐未）我也要「畢業」了 為了參加爸爸的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.17,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛和校長談過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:19.84,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要面對面和敵人打仗的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說之前已經進行過許多次這樣的計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.22,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且無人生還 這次也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼你要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:40.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你…為什麼要約我去海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:41.86,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.65,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算瞞著我一個人消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去！別再靠近我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.62,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（果林）謝謝婆婆 我下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:00.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 乖乖等著學長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.51,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為獎勵 學長們的慰問品分你一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）傳說中的新型{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑體}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（總士）是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（總士）兩個月後計劃終止之前 應該趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）如果我們沒事 就能來迎接我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.10,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:23.07,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 將陵學長 它好像肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.74,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:33.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（果林）欸 為什麼你會吃我餵的麵包？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:37.33,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（果林）我也和你一樣是被人收養的 被皆城家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.00,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（總士）這裡…是以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:46.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑體}起動實驗失敗所產生的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說因為同化現象 全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:54.02,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（總士）稍有不慎 就會被虛無吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也不怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:57.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:04.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}和將陵學長所面對的相比…那些根本不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.05,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）第6次戰鬥時…那件事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:33.51,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）越是乘坐{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑體}駕駛員的肉體越會結晶化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）第8次戰鬥時…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）又有一人倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.78,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）不是敵人 而是本應是武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.11,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（僚）{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑體}…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（工程師）第9至第17區域注水開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（舵手）第1第2第3隔離壁開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:04.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（電腦）逃生程序確認{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fn黑體}啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:08.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（早乙女）想與Festum同歸於盡 銷毀這個島嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.18,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:18.64,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（電腦）{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fn黑體}釋放還有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.04,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:38.79,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.84,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner·Markzwei {\fn黑體}出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等著 我一定把他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:10.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 拜託你…一定要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.40,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Titan-model{\fn黑體}開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.66,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.33,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 停住{\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.79,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能發生了最壞的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.83,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:26.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（公藏）不能讓整座島置身險境 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\fnArial}Markzwei {\fn黑體}停止前進
